=09=09Japan=0F's economy continued its tentative recovery, as GDP grew by 1=
% between=20
April and June compared with the previous quarter, the second consecutive=
=20
quarter of growth. Although it coincided with a big increase in public=20
spending, consumption also rose, giving some hope that the recovery may=20
continue.=20
